The '''Berlin Genesis''' ([[Warsaw]], University Library), designated as Rahlfs 911, is a 3rd or 4th century manuscript on [[papyrus]]. It contains the text of [[Book of Genesis|Genesis]] 1:18-38:5 in [[Greek language|Greek]].

